  "title": "3mths contract to Perm Patient Service Officer (Paragon / Novena) - Up to $2.8K #HKH",
  "description": "<ul><li>Ensure clinic's operational and procedural area readiness based on desired service standards.</li><li>Assist with smooth patient journey including accurate and timely registration, discharge, appointment bookings, cashiering and any other enquiries such as insurance provider's information for billing.</li><li>Provide chaperone assistance to doctors/nurses and prepare consultation documents.</li><li>Attend to any requests, emails and phone enquiries.</li><li>Assist clinic manager in administrative duties.</li><li>Perform any other ad-hoc duties and responsibilities that may be assigned from time to time</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min N / O level</li><li>Training provided </li><li>Experience in healthcare will be an advantage </li></ul><p><strong>3mths contract to Perm </strong></p><p><strong>Up to $2.8K </strong></p><p><br /></p><p><em>Interested candidates, please forward your resume to</em><em><strong> kevynhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p><em>Consultant: Huang Jingsheng Kevyn (R1333338)</em></p><p><em>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)</em></p>",
